text: Zhang Yingying (; born 1983) is a female Chinese former international table tennis player. She won a gold medal and bronze medal at the 1999 World Table Tennis Championships with partners Ma Lin and Zhang Yining, respectively. ==See also== * List of table tennis players ==References== Category:Sportspeople from Nanjing Category:Table tennis players from Jiangsu Category:1983 births Category:Chinese female table tennis players Category:Living people Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Zhang Yingying (table tennis)
